===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|structur|e}}

# To give structure to; to arrange.
#: ''I'm trying to '''structure''' my time better so I'm not always late.''
#: ''I've '''structured''' the deal to limit the amount of money we can lose.''

